room_title: Escape room "Escape the 90's" by The Rooms of BCS in College Station
room_description: Jessica loves the 90's. You could say she's stuck there, and she wants your company.  Locked in her apartment, you will have only one hour to find clues and solve puzzles to unlock the door. Otherwise, the time machine she has been working on for all these years will be activated and you will be sent back for eternity to the 90s, the age of hedgehogs, beepers, singing purple dinosaurs, cassette tapes, and inflatable furniture!
